I know it wasn't Ms. Jones'.

36:28.119 --> 36:29.655
How do you know that?

36:29.755 --> 36:32.424
After you came to my trailer, I
started to worry that Ms. Jones

36:32.524 --> 36:33.625
was in trouble.

36:33.725 --> 36:35.060
That's when I heard
some weird sounds

36:35.160 --> 36:37.396
out by the blind.
When I went to check them out,

36:37.496 --> 36:41.032
I saw Joe putting green bags
into a metal box

36:41.132 --> 36:44.670
right before the same green bags
were found in Debby's blind.

36:44.770 --> 36:48.073
They were out to get Debby
and her land.

36:52.778 --> 36:54.680
No further questions,
Your Honor.

36:54.780 --> 36:56.648
The witness is excused.

36:56.748 --> 36:59.818
Your Honor, in light
of this testimony

36:59.918 --> 37:02.288
and the evidence presented,
the State wishes

37:02.288 --> 37:04.723
to dismiss the charges
against the defendant.

37:04.823 --> 37:06.024
The Court accepts.

37:06.124 --> 37:08.727
<i>State of Oregon v. Debby Jones</i>

37:08.827 --> 37:10.762
is dismissed.

37:10.862 --> 37:15.501
Next on the calendar,
<i>State of Oregon v.</i>

37:15.601 --> 37:17.536
<i>Joe and Sarah Graham.</i>

37:22.674 --> 37:24.209
I'm proud of you.

37:24.310 --> 37:27.713
Thanks. Trying.
Mm-hmm.

37:27.813 --> 37:30.582
